::KitKat::

She smiled and blushes a bit. "Ah...thank you." She couldn't quite 
make this guy out.  It was like he was trying to be suave and kind, 
but something wasn't right.  His actions weren't rehersed or 
practiced. She wondered if he even knew what he was doing? But liked 
his attempts at being kind and found it delightful. She looked at 
Inu.  She put out her hand to him,"Pleased to meet you as well."
